comments.content: It’s a CMYK-image that I can’t see, cause im using Firefox.

It appears to be [ITC Motter Corpus Condensed](http://web.archive.org/web/20080921083315/http:/www.fontshop.com/fonts/singles/elsner_flake/itc_motter_corpus_condensed_regular/?sample_text=Panner&sample_size=74) with some distortion added.
